WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.731 --> 00:00:01.725
Good morning, family!

00:00:01.725 --> 00:00:02.720
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:04.520
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:04.520 --> 00:00:06.445
Well, it's Diana and Brandon again.

00:00:06.445 --> 00:00:10.389
This is my beautiful wife, and I'm thankful she's here with me today.

00:00:10.389 --> 00:00:21.080
She's going to read what Brother Max got in the spirit realm last night—the words—because we were all praying in the spirit and in the interpretation of tongues.

00:00:21.080 --> 00:00:24.977
These are the words that he got from the Lord whenever we were praying.

00:00:24.977 --> 00:00:32.200
When Sister Billie was praying, he was hearing her speaking in tongues, and this is what he interpreted she was saying.

00:00:32.423 --> 00:00:39.027
He has scripture there to back everything, so it's amazing what the Lord was doing last night at the prayer group.

00:00:39.293 --> 00:00:44.074
It was a live prayer call, but we had it at church, and everybody was there gathering and praying.

00:00:45.497 --> 00:00:55.291
It's awesome to see the body of Christ assembled together as one, praying and interceding for the nations.

00:00:56.985 --> 00:00:59.120
There were a lot of live feeds.

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:06.085
If you go through and see the live feeds of churches praying last night, I saw another church praying, and they were interceding over Nashville.

00:01:06.085 --> 00:01:11.924
It's just amazing, folks, that the body of Christ is waking up.

00:01:12.550 --> 00:01:18.400
We all could have been born 150 years ago, and we wouldn't be seeing what we're seeing right now.

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:26.783
You would have already gone home to be with the Lord, but to think that He chose the best for last—I truly believe you're the best He has.

00:01:26.783 --> 00:01:29.880
You were born for such a time as this.

00:01:30.160 --> 00:01:35.420
God has called you, and you, and you—all you that are watching this video right now.

00:01:35.420 --> 00:01:41.869
He has called you and chosen you to be here, born right now, alive in 2025.

00:01:44.020 --> 00:01:53.280
You are praying for this end-time harvest, for this glorious outpouring, for all the things that we're praying over on this channel.

00:01:53.620 --> 00:01:59.080
He's assembling the body together, and it's amazing to see what's going on right now, folks.

00:02:01.503 --> 00:02:07.336
The glorious church is rising up and getting a backbone, saying, 'No more, Satan!

00:02:07.336 --> 00:02:09.519
Thus far and no further.

00:02:09.519 --> 00:02:14.840
You will not do any more damage as long as we're here.

00:02:14.840 --> 00:03:02.040
' That video I did yesterday was really long, but I had an urgency—a prayer urgency—praying for the inauguration coming on the 20th because the enemy is trying to raise his head like that whack-a-mole; you hit it in the head right now.

00:03:11.136 --> 00:03:20.091
You can see he's trying to stir the pot, and we as the body of Christ are going to pray.

00:03:20.091 --> 00:03:34.880
People say, 'Brandon, aren't you scared about what you've been saying on the internet?

00:03:34.880 --> 00:03:37.680
' That would never be me.

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:47.308
That's why He didn't call you to do it.

00:03:47.308 --> 00:03:50.969
That may sound arrogant, but that's why He didn't call you.

00:03:57.200 --> 00:04:25.880
He said, 'Brandon, I called you to come on the internet and say the hard things, things that people will shy away from and be scared to say.

00:04:25.880 --> 00:05:03.660
' But I know that I put a backbone in you, Son, and you're going to say what I tell you to say, and I'll protect you with Big George.

00:05:03.660 --> 00:05:06.720
Who is Big George?

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:48.923
Big George is my angel, and nobody is going to pass Big George because the Bible says in Psalm 91 that He will bear us up in His hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:05:48.923 --> 00:05:56.366
So I dare them.

00:05:56.366 --> 00:06:21.639
The blood of Jesus Christ covers my house, and there is no weapon formed against me or my family that will prosper.

00:06:21.794 --> 00:06:32.172
The Greater One lives on the inside of us.

00:06:45.914 --> 00:06:49.384
You either believe it or you don't.

00:06:50.074 --> 00:07:09.559
You either believe that Jesus is your protector and He said under His wings will you trust, or you don't.

00:07:09.559 --> 00:07:30.160
As for me and my house, to be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:35.493
He said He would protect me.

00:07:36.311 --> 00:08:12.139
I believe, just like David when he was facing the giant and he said, 'Who is this uncircumcised Philistine that he tries to defy the armies of the Lord?

00:08:12.139 --> 00:08:18.670
' Now in these days, ISIS, Al-Qaeda, a terrorist group—they're no different than the Philistines back then.

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:32.719
The same devil that possessed them then is possessing these people now.

00:08:36.611 --> 00:08:38.644
The devil hasn't changed, folks.

00:08:38.644 --> 00:09:21.140
He's the same stupid devil he was back then; he just changed his tactics and methods a little bit because the generations have changed because of the internet and things like that, but he knows how to take people down by fear.

00:09:21.140 --> 00:09:29.669
He comes to kill, steal, and destroy everybody.

00:09:29.669 --> 00:09:47.360
But I'm going to tell you this: the same God that raised Jesus Christ from the dead, the same God that helped Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego go into the fiery furnace, the same God that helped Daniel and Samson with the jawbone, He dwells on the inside of you.

00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:51.320
People go, 'Man, you're bold.

00:09:51.320 --> 00:10:01.131
' Well, why not be bold?

00:10:01.131 --> 00:10:06.604
Do you have confidence in Him?

00:10:06.604 --> 00:10:15.029
My mom is freaking out: 'Brandon, oh my goodness!

00:10:15.029 --> 00:10:34.429
' I'm not trying to pick at people, but I say no, I'm not scared.

00:10:34.429 --> 00:11:05.589
Your flesh gets a little rattled sometimes because you let the devil whisper in your ear, but Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:11:05.589 --> 00:11:20.800
He is a protector, a deliverer, and He is our God in whom I trust.

00:11:20.800 --> 00:11:54.460
That's why He said you need to get Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 deep down in your heart so that you know that He's going to protect you.

00:11:54.460 --> 00:12:05.959
In the video I did yesterday, I went into the spirit.

00:12:05.959 --> 00:12:38.679
If you go back and watch the whole thing, which is an hour and 43 minutes, He showed me more locations.

00:12:38.679 --> 00:12:46.191
He gave me strategic things.

00:12:52.492 --> 00:13:09.240
I saw men walking around, taking pictures, gathering intel, and trying to get ready for their plans against the nation.

00:13:20.626 --> 00:13:20.955
So we pray against those things.

00:13:20.955 --> 00:13:25.662
We pray for covering.

00:13:25.662 --> 00:13:41.320
Sometimes you don't stop everything, but that doesn't mean you don't pray.

00:13:52.653 --> 00:14:08.986
You see things on the news and say, 'Well, did you pray for New Orleans?

00:14:08.986 --> 00:14:19.960
' Yes, we did, but it still happened.

00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:28.531
It could have been a lot worse.

00:14:28.531 --> 00:14:53.628
I always go back to that: when we see dark things happening on the news, we say to ourselves, 'It could have been worse.

00:14:53.628 --> 00:15:01.793
' These are the places the Lord showed me.

00:15:01.793 --> 00:15:47.458
Last night when I was praying, the Lord showed me a lot of locations—ten major cities—and then the Lord told me I was praying over England.

00:15:47.458 --> 00:16:15.209
One of you was really nice and typed up the places that the Lord showed me and made a list.

00:16:21.960 --> 00:16:39.719
This is what she typed up: Las Vegas, Luxor—this is the pyramid—MGM Hotel in Las Vegas, the Eiffel Tower, Statue of Liberty, Trump Tower looking over Central Park.

00:16:47.440 --> 00:16:54.079
I saw the condo windows in there; it was the Trump location.

00:16:54.079 --> 00:17:18.340
She says that he has multiple properties in Miami—three to four properties right now on the beach.

00:17:19.524 --> 00:17:42.760
I saw condos on the beach in Miami and was praying over those.

00:17:50.209 --> 00:17:51.660
Then I went from Miami and I saw Disney.

00:17:55.244 --> 00:18:12.860
I saw a vest on somebody because they couldn't park too close to Disney, and they had to have vests on.

00:18:12.860 --> 00:18:30.240
Then London Bridge, which she says is actually called Tower Bridge, the main bridge in London.

00:18:30.240 --> 00:18:40.044
I was praying over London Bridge and the Vatican.

00:18:40.044 --> 00:18:51.968
The Lord showed me the Vatican, praying over strategic places in Europe and America.

00:18:51.968 --> 00:18:59.475
Tower Bridge connects to the Tower of London.

00:18:59.475 --> 00:19:08.422
Most people mistake Tower Bridge for London Bridge.

00:19:08.422 --> 00:19:26.089
So that's the bridge—it was a big bridge when I was in the spirit.

00:19:26.089 --> 00:19:50.480
The Lord said, 'Pray for this,' and I was thinking, 'What is the point of a terrorist trying to attack these locations like the Statue of Liberty?

00:19:50.480 --> 00:20:06.995
' The Lord said to me, 'Brandon, it's what it represents.

00:20:06.995 --> 00:20:13.520
' It strikes fear.

00:20:13.520 --> 00:20:25.750
Terrorism is just to strike fear in people; it cripples you.

00:20:25.750 --> 00:20:40.944
Fear is so that you do not move and act bold about anything.

00:20:51.947 --> 00:20:52.182
I thought, 'Why Las Vegas?

00:20:52.182 --> 00:21:06.559
' Well, the corruption in Las Vegas, a lot of sin in Las Vegas.

00:21:07.850 --> 00:21:13.179
And then what about Rodeo Drive?

00:21:22.931 --> 00:21:27.724
The Lord told me it was about greed, the lust, and the economy.

00:21:27.724 --> 00:21:51.280
It's about killing, stealing, and destroying, causing people to shrink back and attacking what is so important to a lot of Americans' finances.

00:22:01.733 --> 00:22:02.391
This is the prayer call we had last night.

00:22:02.391 --> 00:22:19.950
There were messages given in tongues, and this was interpreted.

00:22:19.950 --> 00:22:33.195
There was a statement and then scripture to back what was being spoken.

00:22:40.671 --> 00:22:53.200
The Lord was saying in the prayer call that there's a storm coming.

00:23:08.748 --> 00:23:15.279
It says, 'Keep your mind on the prayer and walk in My integrity because you trust in Me.

00:23:15.279 --> 00:23:17.796
' Psalm 55:22.

00:23:17.796 --> 00:23:23.085
'Your safety will come from Me.

00:23:38.663 --> 00:23:39.095
I am faithful.

00:23:45.380 --> 00:23:50.240
I will strengthen and protect from the evil one.

00:23:50.240 --> 00:24:13.760
In this prayer with My prophet and friend, you are My company of prayer to protect your nations from what is coming.

00:24:13.760 --> 00:24:23.560
Keep your eyes on Me.

00:24:23.560 --> 00:24:32.200
' The day of evil is here.

00:24:32.200 --> 00:24:39.853
Understand that I am with you.

00:24:39.853 --> 00:24:42.010
Keep going.

00:24:42.010 --> 00:24:44.039
Take refuge.

00:24:49.760 --> 00:25:10.904
You are to protect them from the evil one and to see the work of your hands all in My name, Church.

00:25:10.904 --> 00:25:22.668
So we are to protect them from the evil ones.

00:25:22.668 --> 00:25:49.615
Our job as the church is to rise up and protect from the evil ones, from rebuking the devourer and standing in the gap, watching on the wall.

00:25:49.615 --> 00:25:53.990
Stand in My glory.

00:26:00.780 --> 00:26:03.140
You have My grace and protection.

00:26:20.369 --> 00:26:20.654
I will save you, My children.

00:26:20.654 --> 00:26:32.341
Just say, 'I will be saved; I will not be afraid.

00:26:32.341 --> 00:26:46.760
' I will not be afraid of the chatter; I will be protected.

00:27:01.015 --> 00:27:02.170
This is the scripture delivered after that message: 1 Peter 5:10, Deuteronomy 31:6, Isaiah, Exodus.

00:27:02.170 --> 00:27:06.960
'My way is perfect.

00:27:12.879 --> 00:27:13.139
I am your shield.

00:27:36.480 --> 00:27:36.940
I will cover you under My wings.

00:27:37.400 --> 00:27:46.057
I am your refuge at all times.

00:27:46.057 --> 00:27:51.693
Take refuge in Me now.

00:27:56.140 --> 00:28:00.520
I will rescue you because I have made you.

00:28:00.520 --> 00:28:12.055
' Thank you, Father, for rescuing us.

00:28:12.055 --> 00:28:16.836
Run to Him now.

00:28:16.836 --> 00:28:25.144
Take refuge in Him.

00:28:25.144 --> 00:28:29.360
Proverbs 3:5, Psalm 16:8.

00:28:29.360 --> 00:28:35.969
'My children, walk in the truth.

00:28:35.969 --> 00:28:39.496
Hold to My word.

00:28:39.496 --> 00:28:40.820
Have fellowship with Me.

00:28:40.820 --> 00:28:41.032
Trust in Me.

00:28:41.032 --> 00:28:43.735
' Praise God!

00:28:43.735 --> 00:28:56.399
You can look all those scriptures up on your own.

00:28:56.399 --> 00:29:03.805
Matches the word of God perfectly.

00:29:10.760 --> 00:29:25.853
The word the Lord gave me for this year was that Justin Trudeau is going to be removed.

00:29:36.719 --> 00:29:49.559
He said, 'Brandon, I've heard the cries of the Canadians, and I'm going to remove the wicked government.

00:29:49.559 --> 00:29:57.333
' I saw a good government.

00:30:08.120 --> 00:30:23.794
I saw that the Conservatives would get the majority, and there would be a glorious outpouring from sea to sea over Canada.

00:30:31.312 --> 00:30:40.400
I saw a major move of God coming for Canada because of the people praying.

00:30:40.400 --> 00:30:47.645
That's why I said don't give up.

00:30:47.645 --> 00:31:02.688
When you start to see a little victory, that is not when you let up.

00:31:07.687 --> 00:31:18.844
You have to run over that thing in the road until it's a greasy spot.

00:31:20.771 --> 00:31:36.170
You do not let up until the buzzer has gone off and you know that you've won.

00:31:36.170 --> 00:32:08.840
We have got to go after this thing like a bulldog on a bone, and I'm not letting go until I get all my victory.

00:32:08.840 --> 00:32:20.463
Some people sent me stuff saying, 'Hey, Brandon, guess what?

00:32:22.159 --> 00:32:26.171
The word's coming to pass.

00:32:26.171 --> 00:32:39.609
' Now we hit it harder because we want revival in Canada.

00:32:58.653 --> 00:32:58.947
The Lord said, 'I'm giving you a window.

00:32:58.947 --> 00:33:15.531
' People say four years is too long; I'm ready to go home now.

00:33:15.531 --> 00:33:27.700
Watch what you say, because the devil's waiting.

00:33:27.700 --> 00:33:37.826
You want to live long and finish strong.

00:33:37.826 --> 00:33:51.119
If you keep saying, 'I'm ready to go home,' you're going to open a door.

00:33:51.119 --> 00:34:19.270
We had a dear sister—I'll be careful and won't say her name—she told us when we met her at the ice cream store, 'I'm ready.

00:34:19.500 --> 00:34:39.919
The Shmita cycle is over, and it's going to be in September, and I'm going home.

00:34:39.919 --> 00:34:50.119
' The Rapture didn't happen, but she went home.

00:34:50.119 --> 00:34:54.963
She got COVID and went home.

00:34:54.963 --> 00:35:05.600
She kept saying it out of her mouth all the time.

00:35:05.600 --> 00:35:18.032
She thought the Rapture was coming, but she went home by the grave.

00:35:18.032 --> 00:35:27.097
You need to watch what you're saying out of your mouth.

00:35:27.097 --> 00:35:39.680
I am going to occupy and finish my race until He comes.

00:35:39.680 --> 00:35:54.500
I will occupy this earth unless I'm old and ready to go home.

00:35:54.500 --> 00:36:07.010
We are snared by the words of our mouth.

00:36:07.010 --> 00:36:18.069
Life and death are in the power of your tongue.

00:36:19.011 --> 00:36:26.608
What you said yesterday is what you're living today.

00:36:30.720 --> 00:36:36.709
You are a product of your words.

00:36:37.714 --> 00:37:07.130
Your tongue has life and death in it, and whatever you're saying out of your mouth, you're going to reap the fruit of it.

00:37:07.130 --> 00:37:28.229
I always say this: 'I am always in the right place at the right time.

00:37:28.229 --> 00:37:57.671
My angels keep charge over me and they bear me up in their hands lest I dash my foot against a stone.

00:37:57.671 --> 00:38:07.897
' Even in divine delays, I thank You, Lord.

00:38:07.897 --> 00:38:25.420
I believe the angels are sent forth to the heirs of salvation to protect us.

00:38:25.420 --> 00:38:36.600
He will always protect and provide for His beloved.

00:38:36.600 --> 00:39:03.960
Maybe you ate Mac and cheese tonight with a peanut butter and jelly sandwich, but you had something in your stomach.

00:39:03.960 --> 00:39:15.654
I remember those little cheeseburgers at McDonald's you could get for 50 cents.

00:39:21.000 --> 00:39:30.280
Now they're like a buck—thanks, Joe Biden—but give God praise for the small things.

00:39:30.280 --> 00:39:42.480
Be thankful for every single miracle in 2025.

00:39:42.480 --> 00:39:53.119
Show the love of God to people.

00:39:53.119 --> 00:39:57.889
Kill them with kindness.

00:40:01.937 --> 00:40:02.263
Love never fails.

00:40:02.263 --> 00:40:11.258
When the angels visited me, they said the most important thing when I get before the Father is, 'What did he do with love?

00:40:11.258 --> 00:40:18.720
' How did he treat the brethren?

00:40:18.720 --> 00:40:44.456
How did he walk in love with the unbeliever?

00:41:02.800 --> 00:41:03.160
That word changed me.

00:41:03.160 --> 00:41:18.569
When people are being cranky or doing me wrong, I just show them love.

00:41:22.099 --> 00:41:25.839
I don't care how they're treating me.

00:41:25.839 --> 00:41:36.107
I've been hated by some of the best nowadays.

00:41:36.107 --> 00:41:44.622
Show them love even if they don't deserve it.

00:41:44.622 --> 00:42:02.152
Pray for them and treat them with respect because it heaps coals of fire on them.

00:42:02.152 --> 00:42:06.788
Vengeance is His.

00:42:06.788 --> 00:42:36.326
If you want to be promoted in life, you've got to walk in love.

00:42:36.326 --> 00:42:59.390
Where is your love walk?

00:42:59.400 --> 00:43:18.280
Faith works by love.

00:43:18.280 --> 00:43:34.240
Be quick to repent.

00:43:34.240 --> 00:44:00.839
I always say I'm sorry.

00:44:00.839 --> 00:44:38.840
If your faith isn't working, check your love walk.

00:44:38.840 --> 00:44:57.800
Sometimes people are hard to deal with, and you have to separate, just like Abraham and Lot.

00:44:57.800 --> 00:45:11.960
Abraham let Lot take the good land first to keep peace.

00:45:11.960 --> 00:45:27.973
He ended up getting the better end of the deal.

00:45:27.973 --> 00:45:49.273
There's blessing in walking in love.

00:46:02.296 --> 00:46:54.992
You don't even know what the devil meant for bad; God will turn it around for good.

00:46:54.992 --> 00:47:11.524
Perfect love casteth out all fear.

00:47:11.524 --> 00:47:37.453
'By this everyone will know that you are My disciples, if you love one another.

00:47:37.453 --> 00:48:58.368
' 'Beloved, let us love one another, for love is of God; and everyone that loveth is born of God and knoweth God.

00:48:58.368 --> 00:49:13.720
He that loveth not knoweth not God, for God is love.

00:49:13.720 --> 00:49:18.520
' 1 John 4:7-8.

00:49:20.240 --> 00:49:29.719
We believe Justin Trudeau is going to be removed.

00:49:30.559 --> 00:49:51.714
The Lord is warning Kim Jong-un and all these other leaders.

00:49:51.714 --> 00:50:01.820
We have a window for a great outpouring.

00:50:01.820 --> 00:50:09.599
Let love flow through your home today.

00:50:09.599 --> 00:50:15.696
We take this communion.

00:50:15.696 --> 00:50:32.747
We thank You, Father, for the body that was broken for us.

00:50:33.193 --> 00:50:52.914
You were wounded for our transgressions, bruised for our iniquities, and with Your stripes we are healed.

00:50:55.920 --> 00:51:11.182
We plead the blood of Jesus Christ over this nation, our houses, and our finances.

00:51:11.182 --> 00:51:16.897
Satan, get your hands off!

00:51:28.057 --> 00:51:28.348
We are blood-bought, born-again believers.

00:51:28.348 --> 00:51:39.097
Every tongue that rises against us, we condemn it.

00:51:45.140 --> 00:51:46.690
We are made righteous by Your blood.

00:51:46.690 --> 00:51:58.579
No weapon formed against us is going to prosper.

00:51:58.579 --> 00:52:29.399
A thousand shall fall at our side and ten thousand at our right hand, but it won't come nigh us.

00:52:39.533 --> 00:52:39.760
We plead the blood of Jesus.

00:52:39.760 --> 00:52:49.195
Holy Spirit, You are welcome in this place.

00:52:49.195 --> 00:53:05.184
Omnipotent Father of mercy and grace, Thou art welcome in this place.

00:53:05.184 --> 00:53:22.319
For in Your presence, there’s healing divine; no other power can save, Lord, but Thine.

00:53:22.319 --> 00:53:24.674
Receive it.

00:53:24.674 --> 00:53:36.063
The Lord told me there are healings coming on you all right now.

00:53:36.063 --> 00:53:43.180
You're being delivered from this demonic assignment.

00:53:43.180 --> 00:53:50.670
Reach out and receive it by faith.

00:53:50.670 --> 00:53:55.547
'It's mine, I take it now.

00:53:55.547 --> 00:54:02.571
' Oh, the glory is here!

00:54:03.184 --> 00:54:16.300
I can sense His mighty presence in the very atmosphere.

00:54:16.300 --> 00:54:27.929
2025 is the time that I'm going to draw near.

00:54:41.189 --> 00:54:41.504
We believe this is the year of the baby.

00:54:41.504 --> 00:54:54.773
People who haven't been able to have them will have them this year.

00:54:54.773 --> 00:55:14.228
I speak over their wombs in the name of Jesus that they are healed, whole, and well.

00:55:15.651 --> 00:55:40.935
We thank You that they will be able to carry them to full term with no miscarriages.

00:55:40.935 --> 00:55:48.049
These babies are whole and healed.

00:55:50.329 --> 00:56:08.634
We thank You that they are neurotypical, they have healthy hearts, and they are knit in the womb.

00:56:08.634 --> 00:56:19.107
